2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECape%20Coral%3C%2Fa%3E%2011%20years%20ago%20after%20four%20of%20her%20five%20kids%20moved%20there.%20Her%20kids%20loved%20the%20weather%2C%20the%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20and%20the%20cheaper%20housing%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20settled%20on%20Cape%20Coral%20for%20the%20beach%20access%20and%20warm%20weather%2C%20and%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20they%20made%20the%20most%20of%20their%20time%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Cape%20Coral%20had%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20rates%20of%20foreclosures%20in%20the%20US%2C%20meaning%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20got%20a%20good%20deal%20on%20their%20home.%20They%20built%20a%20five-bedroom%2C%20four-and-a-half-bath%20home%20with%20a%20three-car%20garage%20and%20saltwater%20swimming%20pool.%20They%20built%20the%20home%20for%20about%20%24375%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20we%20built%20a%20gorgeous%20home%2C%20never%20thinking%20we%20would%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%20%E2%80%9COur%20builder%20was%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20best%20friend.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20said%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20anticipate%20the%20costs%20of%20home%20upkeep%20in%20Florida.%20The%20heat%20and%20humidity%20got%20worse%20and%20worse%20every%20year%2C%20she%20said%2C%20which%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20her%20house.%20She%20had%20to%20pay%20lawn%20service%20workers%2C%20landscapers%2C%20pool%20people%2C%20and%20pest%20control.%20She%20also%20had%20to%20install%20a%20home%20water%20system%20since%20she%20said%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20was%20not%20drinkable%20and%20ruined%20her%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20electric%20bill%20was%20consistently%20over%20%24200%20monthly%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%24300%20in%20the%20summers.%20Her%20water%20bill%20was%20consistently%20over%20%24100%20a%20month.%20She%20said%20her%20car%2C%20homeowners%2C%20and%20flood%20insurance%20have%20also%20shot%20up%20recently%20and%20were%20much%20more%20than%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffarmers-insurance-florida-stops-home-auto-insurance-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehome%20insurance%20providers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomeowners-california-florida-insurance-issues-natural-disasters-wildfires-hurricanes-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eleft%20Florida%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20altogether%20or%20moved%20from%20the%20coast%20to%20former%20inland%2C%20despite%20efforts%20by%20state%20lawmakers%20to%20make%20the%20market%20more%20stable.%20Per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iii.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocs%2Fpdf%2Ftriple-i_trends_and_insights_florida_pc_02152023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInsurance%20Information%20Institute%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20annual%20premium%20in%20Florida%20rose%20to%20over%20%244%2C200%2C%20triple%20the%20national%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGood%20god%2C%20the%20sun%20was%20so%20strong.%20We%20had%20to%20have%20the%20whole%20outside%20of%20our%20house%20repainted%20before%20we%20moved%20because%20it%20fades%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20heat%20was%20often%20unbearable%20in%20the%20warmer%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20crowded%20when%20we%20moved%2C%20but%20now%20they%E2%80%99re%20building%20on%20every%20available%20inch%2C%20and%20the%20price%20of%20the%20homes%20is%20insane%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20lucky%20since%20we%20sold%20our%20house%20six%20months%20before%20Hurricane%20Ian.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20hurricane%20severely%20impacted%20many%20people%20she%20knew%20and%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20rebuild%20their%20homes%20or%20reopen%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20also%20left%20and%20went%20back%20to%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20she%20went%20down%20with%20her%20husband%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%20and%20said%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20recognize%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20so%20different%20since%20the%20hurricane%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20politics%20in%20her%20area%20also%20made%20her%20feel%20out%20of%20place.%20She%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20made%20many%20good%20friends%20they%20often%20visit%2C%20but%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20handle%20the%20%E2%80%9Cin%20your%20face%E2%80%9D%20politics%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20planning%20when%20to%20leave%2C%20Nancy%20and%20her%20husband%20sold%20their%20home%20for%20%24700%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20they%20were%20giving%20us%20that%20much%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20it%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-out-of-florida-relocated-to-georgia-texas-north-carolina-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaway%20we%20went%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20back%20to%20Virginia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcamryn-spina-moved-florida-virginia-new-job-never-hired-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20Virginia%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%202022%2C%20settling%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20southwest%20near%20Virginia%20Tech.%20While%20still%20living%20in%20Florida%2C%20Nancy%20and%20her%20husband%20bought%20a%20small%20townhouse%20for%20%24127%2C000%2C%20which%20they%20owned%20for%20three%20years%20before%20selling%20it%20for%20%24215%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20was%20an%20805-square-foot%20two-bedroom%2C%20one-bathroom%20townhouse%20with%20wood%20floors%2C%20gas%20heat%2C%20and%20a%20fireplace.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20much%20easier%20to%20maintain%20this%20home%2C%20and%20upkeep%20prices%20were%20small%20compared%20to%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20recently%20bought%20their%20current%20Virginia%20home%20for%20%24560%2C000%2C%20which%20has%20everything%20she%20wanted.%20Her%20home%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20big%20as%20the%20Florida%20home%2C%20but%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20break%20the%20bank%20for%20them%20and%20is%20in%20a%20quieter%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20daughters%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20happy%20about%20their%20decision%2C%20but%20Nancy%20was%20sure%20the%20move%20was%20right.%20She%20added%20she%20never%20wants%20to%20live%20by%20the%20water%20again%2C%20as%20she%E2%80%99s%20paying%20a%20lot%20less%20in%20insurance%20and%20maintenance%20costs%20in%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20in%20a%20rural%20area%2C%20very%20conservative%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20my%20face%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20have%20Virginia%20Tech%20on%20one%20side%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%2010%20minutes%20from%20Radford%20University%2C%20so%20we%20have%20young%20people%20here%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20said%20she%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20moving%2C%20as%20she%20enjoys%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20the%20minimal%20traffic%2C%20and%20the%20small-town%20feel%20of%20her%20area.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20go%20to%20lots%20of%20sporting%20events%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realize%20how%20much%20more%20I%20paid%20for%20things%20until%20I%20left%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20gas%20heat%2C%20and%20the%20bill%20is%20next%20to%20nothing%2C%20even%20in%20the%20summer%20with%20my%20air%20conditioning.%20My%20house%20is%20a%20little%20over%203%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20little%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20said%20living%20in%20her%20part%20of%20Virginia%20is%20much%20cheaper%20than%20in%20Cape%20Coral%2C%20particularly%20on%20utilities.%20She%20said%20her%20car%20insurance%20is%20half%20as%20expensive%20as%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20she%20said%20her%20car%20registration%20fees%20in%20Virginia%20were%20way%20lower.%20She%20acknowledged%20that%20homeowners%20insurance%20may%20be%20similarly%20high%20between%20Cape%20Coral%20and%20Fairfax%20County%2C%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20counties%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20miss%20my%20Florida%20house%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20great%20if%20it%20was%20up%20here%2C%20but%20we%20made%20the%20right%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nancy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20state%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-virginia-pros-cons-cape-coral-weather-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708339381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd310a94aa8ee8e84b7ce2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-virginia-pros-cons-cape-coral-weather-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nancy%2C%20a%2068-year-old%20retiree%2C%20moved%20back%20to%20a%20rural%20home%20in%20Virginia%20from%20Florida%20due%20to%20escalating%20costs%2C%20the%20heat%2C%20and%20overbearing%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-virginia-pros-cons-cape-coral-weather-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22European%20Film%20Market%20Sees%20Dealmaking%20Rebound%20Post-Strikes%20for%20Splashy%20U.S.%20Packages%20and%20Select%20Interna