%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fred-tape-culture-in-up-has-been-replaced-by-red-carpet-culture-pm-modi-at-groundbreaking-ceremony-for-investment-plans-5086699%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fred-tape-culture-in-up-has-been-replaced-by-red-carpet-culture-pm-modi-at-groundbreaking-ceremony-for-investment-plans-5086699%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fred-tape-culture-in-up-has-been-replaced-by-red-carpet-culture-pm-modi-at-groundbreaking-ceremony-for-investment-plans-5086699%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Compare%20It%20To%20Manipur%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Sandeshkhali%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20denied%20admission%20to%20a%20petition%20seeking%20a%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20the%20Sandeshkali%20case%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20petition%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20lawyer%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20was%20turned%20down%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20prompting%20the%20petitioner%20to%20withdraw%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Augustin%20George%20Masih%2C%20expressed%20reservations%20about%20comparing%20the%20Sandeshkali%20case%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20emphasized%20that%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20already%20taken%20suo-motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20is%20best%20suited%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20and%20order%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20has%20taken%20the%20initiative%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20independently.%20Recognizing%20its%20capability%20to%20order%20an%20SIT%20investigation%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20aims%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%2C%20withdrew%20the%20plea%2C%20allowing%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20case.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20permission%20for%20this%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20the%20Manipur%20model%2C%20proposed%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20committee%20consisting%20of%20three%20retired%20judges%20from%20different%20states%20to%20oversee%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20investigation%20into%20the%20Sandeshkali%20case.%20This%20suggestion%20aligns%20with%20the%20demands%20for%20an%20unbiased%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlakh%20Alok%20Srivastava%2C%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20victims%2C%20filed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20PIL%20not%20only%20demanded%20compensation%20for%20the%20victims%20but%20also%20called%20for%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20the%20culpable%20police%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20NDTV's%20investigation%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20complex%20nature%20of%20the%20Sandeshkali%20case.%20While%20the%20BJP%20alleges%20sexual%20assault%2C%20women%20interviewed%20by%20NDTV%20hinted%20at%20a%20more%20nuanced%20reality.%20They%20spoke%20of%20being%20summoned%20to%20the%20BJP%20office%20and%20facing%20threats%20for%20non-compliance%2C%20though%20they%20were%20reluctant%20to%20reveal%20their%20identities%20on%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20escalated%20further%20when%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20President%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20reportedly%20suffered%20injuries%20during%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police%20while%20attempting%20to%20reach%20Sandeshkhali.%20The%20BJP%20claims%20their%20visit%20aimed%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20alleged%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708338060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcq5c2cmg_supreme-court-reuters_625x300_06_Februar