20board%20will%20shortly%20decide%20on%20candidates%20for%20the%20union%20territory's%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20which%20are%20split%20between%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(in%20power%20at%20the%20centre)%20and%20the%20National%20Conference%20of%20another%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Farooq%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20they%20(the%20National%20Conference)%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20decision...%20we%20will%20discuss%20it.%20There%20will%20be%20deliberations%20and%20a%20future%20course%20of%20action%20will%20be%20decided%20(soon)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PDP's%20Suhail%20Bukhari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20said%20the%20NC%20would%20fight%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20on%20its%20own%20steam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20caused%20a%20flutter%20given%20INDIA%20is%20scrambling%20for%20survival%20after%20being%20dumped%20by%20founder%20and%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20and%20snubbed%20by%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20And%20today%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%20dropped%20its%20own%20ultimatum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20alliance%20is%20expected%20to%20lose%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20despite%20the%20outfit%20having%20agreed%20a%20deal%20last%20month%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20shortly%20after%20Farooq%20Abdullah's%20comment%2C%20his%20son%2C%20also%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20the%20National%20Conference%20will%20remain%20a%20part%20of%20INDIA%20and%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20heads%20the%20group%2C%20for%20three%20of%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20part%20of%20INDIA%20and%20still%20are...%20things%20have%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20The%20main%20idea%20of%20the%20grouping%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%2C%20for%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20sailing%20in%20two%20boats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooq%20Abdullah's%20comment%20-%20%26quot%3Bthere%20should%20be%20no%20questions%20on%20this%20alliance%20anymore...%26quot%3B%20-%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20give%20the%20three-time%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20a%20supporter%20and%20attended%20all%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20though%2C%20he%20his%20concern%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus%20within%20the%20bloc%20on%20seat-sharing%20deals%2C%20worries%20also%20flagged%20earlier%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20and%20others%2C%20including%20Mr%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%20we%20have%20to%20forget%20(our)%20differences...%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20criticise%20its%20rivals%2C%20with%20party%20spokesperson%20RS%20Pathania%20telling%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20ragtag%20conglomerate%20in%20which%20participants%20have%20least%20convergence%20on%20any%20issues%20of%20policy%2C%20agenda%20or%20manifesto.%20The%20alliance%20almost%20falls%20(apart)%20like%20a%20house%20of%20cards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP's%20move%20comes%20days%20after%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20declared%20his%20party%2C%20while%20remaining%20part%20of%20the%20under-pressure%20INDIA%20grouping%2C%20%26quot%3Bwill%20contest%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20strength%26quot%3B.%20Sources%20said%20this%20call%20was%20based%20on%20an%20internal%20assessment%20that%20said%20the%20party%20could%20win%20at%20least%20three%20seats%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20is%20unwilling%20to%20give%20up%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%2