mated%20record%20346.13%20lakh%20tons%20of%20maize%20was%20grown%20in%202022%2F23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20MSP%20Scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%20MSP%20is%20offered%20on%2023%20crops%20apart%20from%20staples%20like%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20pulses%2C%20and%20maize.%20These%20include%20ragi%2C%20groundnut%2C%20soybean%2C%20sunflower%20seeds%2C%20barley%2C%20rapeseed%2C%20and%20mustard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20prices%20were%20announced%20in%20June%2C%20when%20kharif%20crop%20MSPs%20were%20increased%20-%20and%20fixed%20at%20a%20level%20at%20least%201.5%20times%20the%20All-India%20weighted%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20-%C2%A0%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20remunerative%20prices%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20to%20encourage%20crop%20diversification%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers'%20MSP%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20legal%20backing%20for%20MSPs%2C%20the%20farmers%20want%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20as%20well%20as%20pension%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%20on%20MSP%20are%20worth%20mentioning%2C%20since%20it%20suggested%20the%20floor%20price%20be%20set%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20above%20the%20weighted%20average%20cost%20of%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-set-for-mega-delhi-chalo-march-what-are-the-key-demands-5047380%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20Are%20Key%20Demands%20Of%20Farmers%20That%20Remain%20Unresolved%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20known%20as%20the%20C2%2B50%20formula%2C%20which%20factors%20cost%20of%20capital%20and%20land%20rent%20in%20setting%20MSPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20umbrella%20farmer%20body%20behind%20this%20round%20of%20protests%2C%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20has%20indicated%20it%20is%20unwilling%20to%20accept%20anything%20less%20than%20that%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20MSP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSP%20is%20a%20form%20of%20market%20intervention%20and%20refers%20to%20a%20set%20fixed%20by%20the%20government%20to%20protect%20farmers%20from%20a%20steep%20fall%20in%20crop%20prices%3B%20for%20example%2C%20during%20a%20bumper%20crop%20when%20prices%20plummet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20every%20year%20the%20government%20purchases%20a%20quantity%20of%20certain%20crops%2C%20the%20list%20and%20prices%20of%20which%20are%20announced%20before%20sowing.%20The%20purpose%20is%20not%20only%20to%20allow%20farmers%20a%20minimum%20return%20on%20(part%20of)%20their%20investment%20but%20also%20procure%20crops%20for%20the%20government's%20public%20distribution%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSP%20is%20the%20floor%20price%2C%20i.e.%2C%20it%20is%20the%20minimum%20at%20which%20a%20crop%20can%20be%20bought%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Archives%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarm-laws-scrapped-farm-laws-to-be-cancelled-says-pm-modi-what-are-the-three-black-laws-2617490%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarm%20Laws%20To%20Be%20Scrapped.%20What%20Are%20Three%20%26quot%3BBlack%26quot%3B%20Laws%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSPs%2C%20however%2C%20have%20no%20legal%20backing%2C%20meaning%20the%20government%20is%20not%20obliged%20to%20buy%2C%20for%20example%2C%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20a%20farmer's%20paddy%20crop%20at%20the%20floor%20price.%20And%20it%20is%20this%20that%20the%20farmers%20want%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20MSP%20made%20headlines%20four%20years%20ago%20after%20the%20second%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20three%20%26quot%3Bblack%26quot%3B%20laws%2C%20which%20were%20scrapped%20after%20the%20farmers'%202020%2F21%20protest.%20This%20law%20-%20the%20Farmers%20(Empowerment%20and%20Protection)%20Agreement%20of%20Price%20Assurance%20and%20Farm%20Services%20Act%20-%20said%20crop%20prices%20would%20be%20determined%20by%20market%20forces%20-%20i.e.%2C%20farmers%20would%20get%20more%20for%20in-demand%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%2C%20however%2C%20felt%20this%20would%20abolish%2C%20by%20default%2C%20the%20MSP%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-misinformation-being-spread-that-farmers-wont-get-right-prices-amid-protests-over-farm-bills-2297418%3Fpfrom%3Dhome-topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20sought%2C%20unsuccessfully%2C%20to%20allay%20these%20fears%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers'%20Other%20Demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20farmers%20also%20want%20debt%20waivers%2C%20no%20hike%20in%20electricity%20tariffs%2C%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20filed%20in%20the%202020%2F21%20protests%2C%20when%20they%20had%20violent%20clashes%20with%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20they%20also%20want%20justice%20for%20farmers%20killed%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20and%20compensation%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Are%20The%20Farmers%20Now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesting%20farmers%20are%20now%20camped%20around%20200%20km%20from%20Delhi%2C%20with%20multiple%20fortifications%20and%20barriers%20-%20from%20concrete%20blocks%20and%20barbed%20wire%20to%20nail%20strips%20and%20metal%20barricades%20-%20in%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%2C%20for%20now%2C%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%20crossing%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshambhu-borde