usinessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-fashion-trends-workers-return-to-office-rto-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20workwear%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20demonstrated%20in%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40maree_ellard%2Fvideo%2F7294228521696644359%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETikTok%20video%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%2C%20when%20wearing%20a%20mini%20skirt%20to%20work%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20bend%20down%20or%20sit%20without%20showing%20too%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can't%20functionally%20move%2C%20and%20you're%20only%20basing%20your%20outfit%20on%20just%20standing%20straight%20%E2%80%94%20you%20need%20to%20cut%20that%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ellard%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20rule%20applies%20to%20tops%20and%20pants%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20outfits%20will%20only%20add%20to%20your%20everyday%20stress%20because%20it%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20mental%20power%20to%20maneuver%20in%20them%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Liz%20Teich%20in%20a%20corporate%20outfit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3b1027a3d271488788e47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiz%20Teich%20in%20a%20corporate%20outfit.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Teich%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EMen%20should%20avoid%20wearing%20shorts%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiz%20Teich%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20stylist%2C%20said%20that%20this%20advice%20can%20apply%20to%20men%20as%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20shorts%20rarely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-comfortable-performance-workwear-brands-for-office%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elook%20professional%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20men%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20explained%20that%20air%20conditioning%20in%20the%20office%20negates%20the%20fact%20th