%20of%20a%20senior%20leader%20in%20a%20midsize%20New%20York%20firm%20who%20was%20bemused%20after%20a%20junior%20worker%20showed%20up%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-on%20crop%20top%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20weirded%20out%20by%20it%2C%20and%20the%20people%20on%20my%20team%20were%2C%20too.%20I%20know%20because%20several%20people%20told%20me%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20this%20young%20woman's%20boss%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20vented%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20should%20say%20something%20to%20her.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20crush%20her%20spirit%20or%20make%20her%20feel%20embarrassed.%20I%20also%20don't%20want%20to%20provoke%20a%20lawsuit.%20What's%20the%20tactful%20approach%20to%20this%20issue%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20poor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-casual-what-not-to-wear-to-work-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffice%20clothing%3C%2Fa%3E%20choices%20could%20hurt%20younger%20workers'%20career%20progression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20somebody's%20dressed%20kind%20of%20sloppily%2C%20we%20might%20make%20the%20inference%20that%20they're%20not%20all%20that%20conscientious%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Vogel%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Fox%20School%20of%20Business%20at%20Temple%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20put%20themselves%20together%2C%20their%20bosses%20might%20conclude%20that%20they%20also%20wouldn't%20take%20the%20time%20to%20put%20a%20key%20piece%20of%20work%20together%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-office-fashion-attire-workwear-not-appropriate-revealing-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708333201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb532c6fcb546d2d4eee9e%3