0as%20a%20school%20stood%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20village.%20The%20land%20around%20it%2C%20where%20the%20Maoists%20grew%20vegetables%2C%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20area%20spanning%20kilometres%20used%20to%20be%20Maoist%20training%20camps%2C%20where%20they%20also%20held%20meetings%20and%20recruited%20young%20villagers%20living%20in%20nearby%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20provided%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20banned%20group%20functioned%20and%20carried%20out%20heinous%20attacks%20on%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20of%20a%20security%20camp%20in%20the%20village%20delivers%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20Maoists.%20In%20an%20area%20where%20the%20cops%20once%20feared%20to%20set%20foot%20on%2C%20seven%20such%20camps%20have%20opened%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months%20and%20are%20going%20to%20help%20their%20ongoing%20war%20against%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20significance%20of%20this%20camp%20is%20that%20a%20security%20team%20can%20be%20dispatched%20from%20here%20whenever%20there's%20information%20about%20Maoist%20movement%2C%20unlike%20before%20when%20it%20took%20them%20hours%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20village%2C%20the%20Sukma%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20met%20Hidma's%20mother%20and%20assured%20her%20help%20in%20every%20possible%20way.%20Urging%20the%20villagers%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20Maoist%20activities%2C%20he%20said%20the%20benefits%20of%20all%20government%20schemes%20will%20be%20extended%20them.%20Development%20of%20the%20village%20is%20possible%20only%20with%20the%20cooperation%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20move%20comes%20weeks%20after%20three%20CRPF%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20during%20a%20Maoist%20attack%20on%20the%20Tekalguda%20police%20camp.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20soldiers%20were%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20January%2030%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pu