atta%20to%20celebrate%20the%20PPP's%20election%20victory%20in%20Sindh%20province%2C%20Bilawal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20told%20%5Bby%20PML-N%5D%20that%20let%20us%20be%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20three%20years%20and%20then%20you%20can%20take%20the%20premiership%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20no%20to%20this.%20I%20said%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20prime%20minister%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20it%20would%20be%20after%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20elect%20me.%E2%80%9D%20Without%20taking%20any%20names%2C%20Bilawal%20said%20the%20party%20had%20decided%20that%20it%20would%20move%20forward%20with%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20who%20have%20asked%20for%20its%20votes%E2%80%9D%20and%20would%20not%20seek%20any%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilawal%20also%20said%20his%20father%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20would%20be%20the%20PPP's%20candidate%20for%20president%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20former%20president%20would%20play%20his%20role%20to%20defuse%20political%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20control%20the%20fire%20spreading%20in%20the%20country%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20Zardari%20will%20be%20our%20candidate%20for%20the%20presidential%20election.%20And%20when%20he%20takes%20up%20the%20post%2C%20he%20will%20put%20out%20this%20fire%2C%20and%20will%20save%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20provinces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20country%20needed%20a%20political%20party%20that%20talked%20about%20people's%20problems%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20brewing%20economic%20and%20political%20crisis%20had%20divided%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20should%20happen%20is%20that%20politicians%20and%20all%20political%20parties%20should%20think%20about%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20their%20personal%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bilawal%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20a%20PTI-backed%20candidate%20was%20made%20to%20win%20against%20a%20PPP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20PPP%20had%20decided%20to%20collect%20the%20election%20complaints%20of%20party%20workers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20and%20raise%20them%20at%20appropriate%20forums.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20unsuccessful%2C%20we%20will%20come%20to%20you%20and%20protest%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilawal%20appealed%20to%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstay%20within%20the%20system%E2%80%9D%20and%20work%20for%20the%20country's%20betterment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Bilawal's%20comments%2C%20PML-N%20leader%20Ishaq%20Dar%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20not%20appropriate%20to%20divulge%20details%20about%20talks%20between%20the%20parties%20vying%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20insisted%20that%20the%20PPP%20chairman%20had%20made%20the%20time-sharing%20formula%20public%20but%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20was%20just%20one%20aspect%20and%20there%20can%20be%20more%20formulas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%20said%20the%20plan%20to%20form%20a%20government%20with%20the%20PPP%20and%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20%E2%80%93%20Pakistan%20(MQM-P)%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstill%20on%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20was%20no%20other%20choice%20available%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20finance%20minister%20said%20the%20committees%20of%20both%20political%20parties%20had%20held%20four%20rounds%20of%20meetings%20so%20far%20but%20nothing%20was%20finalised%20as%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20the%20committee%20members%20of%20both%20parties%20will%20make%20anything%20public%20till%20it%20isn't%20final%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20receive%20calls%20daily%20to%20find%20out%20about%20the%20progress%20but%20I%20am%20morally%20bound%20to%20not%20say%20anything%20till%20it's%20finalised%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20upcoming%20meeting%2C%20marking%20the%20fifth%20round%20between%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20although%20he%20refrained%20from%20divulging%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsultation%20on%20various%20proposals%20was%20underway%20till%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20Dar%20stated%20in%20a%20post%20shared%20by%20PML-N%20on%20X%2C%20suggesting%20ongoing%20deliberations%20between%20the%20parties.%20He%20further%20remarked%20that%20while%20progress%20had%20been%20made%2C%20both%20sides%20had%20yet%20to%20finalise%20key%20points%20of%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20towards%20consensus%20on%20critical%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Dar%20affirmed%2C%20underlining%20the%20parties'%20efforts%20to%20forge%20a%20joint%20declaration%20regarding%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20next%20government%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20have%20already%20been%20controversial%20with%20several%20serious%20allegations%20of%20widespread%20rigging%20to%20change%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%20and%20his%20party%20have%20rejected%20the%20results%20claiming%20they%20had%20won%20at%20least%20180%20seats%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%20and%20have%20called%20for%20peaceful%20protests%20throughout%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Balochistan%20province%2C%20several%20political%20parties%20have%20completely%20rejected%20the%20election%20results%20and%20have%20launched%20an%20indefinite%20shutter%20down%2C%20wheel%20jam%20campaign%20and%20also%20disrupted%20the%20traffic%20movement%20on%20the%20national%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20PTI%20on%20Sunday%20renewed%20its%20efforts%20to%20form%20governments%20in%20the%20Centre%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20new%20partner%2C%20the%20Sunni%20Ittehad%20Council%20(SIC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20its%20decision%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20opposition%20benches%20and%20launch%20a%20countrywide%20campaign%20against%20alleged%20rigging%20in%20the%20Feb%208%20elections%2C%20In%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20the%20talks%20between%20the%20PTI%20Parliamentarians%20stalled%20after%20the%20PTI%20leadership%20demanded%20the%20removal%20of%20certain%20leaders%2C%20including%20ex-CMs%20Pervez%20Khattak%20and%20Mahmood%20Khan%20from%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Sunday%2C%20PTI%20leaders%20vowed%20to%20form%20governments%2C%20with%20its%20prime%20minister%20slot%20candidate%20Omar%20Ayub%20saying%20that%2030%20million%20votes%20were%20polled%20for%20PTI-backed%20candidates%20even%20without%20its%20electoral%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%98bat'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20its%20numbers%20in%20parliament%2C%20the%20PTI%20after%20talks%20in%20Islamabad%20decided%20in%20principle%20to%20become%20partners%20with%20the%20Sunni%20Ittehad%20Council%20(SIC)%20in%20the%20National%20and%20Punjab%20assemblies%20to%20claim%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708331160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fla0o2tdo_bilawal-bhutto-_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbilawal-bhutto-explains-why-he-did-not-accept-pakistan-pm-post-5085957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20Chairman%20Bilawal%20Bhutto-Zardari%20has%20revealed%20that%20he%20said%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20power-sharing%20formula%20in%20which%20the%20prime%20ministers%20post%20would%20be%20shared%20between%20his%20and%20former%20premier%20Nawaz%20Sharif's%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbilawal-b