2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20Country%20Is%20Difficult%20As%20A%20Woman%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Coach%20Alleges%20Discrimination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJanneke%20Schopman%2C%20the%20Indian%20women's%20hockey%20team%20coach%2C%20has%20made%20some%20serious%20allegations%20against%20Hockey%20India%2C%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fhockey%2Findias-women-hockey-coach-janneke-schopman-hits-out-didnt-feel-like-i-was-valued-by-hockey-india-9168584%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Janneke%20Schopman%20gave%20the%20interview%20on%20Sunday%20after%20India%20defeated%20USA%202-1%20in%20their%20final%20match%20of%20the%20Rourkela%20leg%20of%20the%20FIH%20Hockey%20Pro%20League%202023%2F24%20at%20the%20Birsa%20Munda%20Hockey%20Stadium.%20Janneke%2C%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20medallist%20with%20the%20Netherlands%20in%202008%2C%20started%20as%20an%20analytical%20coach%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%202020%20and%20was%20subsequently%20made%20the%20chief%20coach%20after%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanneke%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%2C%20broke%20down%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20while%20speaking%20about%20her%20day-to-day%20challenges%20in%20the%20top%20job%20and%20dealing%20with%20Hockey%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20hard%2C%20very%20hard.%20Because%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20come%20from%20a%20culture%20where%20women%20are%20respected%20and%20valued.%20I%20don't%20feel%20that%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanneke%20Schopman%2C%2046%2C%20added%20she%20felt%20'alone%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years'%20and%20claimed%20claimed%20she%20wasn't%20'valued%20and%20respected'%20by%20her%20employers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20I%20was%20the%20assistant%20coach%20some%20people%20wouldn't%20even%20look%20at%20me%20or%20wouldn't%20acknowledge%20me%20or%20wouldn't%20respond%20and%20then%20you%20become%20the%20chief%20coach%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20people%20are%20interested%20in%20you.%20I%20struggled%20a%20lot%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20the%20difference%20at%20how%20men's%20coaches%20are%20treated...%20between%20me%20and%20the%20men's%20coach%2C%20or%20the%20girls%20and%20the%20men's%20team%2C%20just%20in%20general.%20They%20(the%20women%20players)%20never%20complain%20and%20they%20work%20so%20hard.%20I%20shouldn't%20speak%20for%20them%20so%20I%20won't.%20I%20love%20them.%20I%20think%20they%20work%20so%20hard%2C%20they%20do%20what%20I%20ask%2C%20they%20wanna%20learn%2C%20wanna%20do%20new%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Schopman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20for%20me%20personally%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20having%20worked%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20this%20country%20is%20extremely%20difficult%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20coming%20from%20a%20culture%20where%2C%20yeah%2C%20you%20can%20have%20an%20opinion%20and%20it's%20valued.%20It's%20really%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20should%20have%20left%20after%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%202022%20where%20India%20won%20the%20bronze%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20asked%20my%20family%2C%20I%20should%20have%20left%20after%20a%20year.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20I%20should%20have%20left%20after%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20because%20it%20was%20too%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20manage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanneke%20future%20with%20the%20Indian%20women's%20hockey%20team%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20speculation%20since%20the%20side%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20in%20January%20after%20finishing%20fourth%20in%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20know%20it's%20tough.%20But%20like%20I%20said%2C%20I%20love%20the%20girls%20and%20I%20see%20so%20much%20potential.%20But%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20for%20me%20as%20an%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20Janneke%20said%20if%20she%20will%20stay%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20hockey%20federation%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708327260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fjlt35q7g_janneke-schopman_625x300_19_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fhockey%2Fthis-country-is-extremely-difficult-as-a-woman-india-womens-hockey-coach-alleges-serious-discrimination-5085867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Janneke%20Schopman%2C%20the%20first%20woman%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%2C%20broke%20down%20while%20speaking%20about%20her%20day-to-day%20challenges%20in%20the%20top%20job%20and%20dealing%20with%20Hockey%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20Announces%20Plans%20To%20Build%20Homes%20For%20Homeless%20On%20His%20Estate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritain's%20Prince%20Willaim%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20build%20on%20his%20own%20land%20to%20tackle%20homelessness.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20project%20will%20provide%2024%20homes%20on%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall%20land%20-%20a%20private%20estate%20which%2C%20as%20per%20the%20official%20site%2C%20funds%20the%20public%2C%20charitable%20and%20private%20activities%20of%20the%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20and%20his%20family.%20The%20construction%20of%20the%20homes%20will%20begin%20in%20September%20and%20the%20first%20homes%20are%20due%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20autumn%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20homes%20will%20be%20built%20in%20partnership%20with%20homelessness%20charity%20St%20Petrocs.%20The%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20development%20will%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20high-quality%20temporary%20accommodation%20that%20feels%20like%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-cornwall-68330944%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20statement%20also%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bwrap-around%20support%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20provided%20by%20St%20Petrocs%20to%20help%20residents%20access%20training%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBen%20Murphy%2C%20Duchy's%20estate%20director%2C%20said%20that%20homes%20would%20help%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20the%20cycle%20of%20homelessness%20in%20the%20Newquay%20area%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAs%20one%20of%20his%20key%20priorities%20for%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall%2C%20Prince%20William%20asked%20us%20to%20address%20the%20homelessness%20challenge%20within%20Cornwall%20and%20other%20areas%20where%20the%20estate%20resides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Duchy%20is%20well-known%20for%20integrating%20high%20quality%20affordable%20housing%20into%20the%20new%20communities%20built%20on%20its%20land%2C%20and%20Prince%20William%20is%20determined%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20housing%20crisis.%20The%20shortage%20of%20social%20rent%20and%20private%20rented%20properties%20are%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20main%20causes%20of%20increasing%20homelessness%20across%20the%20country%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20launch%20this%20project%20alongside%20ambitious%20plans%20to%20unlock%20more%20affordable%20and%20attainable%20homes%20across%20our%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murphy%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20charity%20St%20Petrocs%20said%20it%20would%20help%20residents%20access%20training%20and%20employment%20%26quot%3Bto%20provide%20a%20route%20out%20of%20homelessness%20for%20good%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20charity%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Cornwall%20for%20over%2030%20years%20and%20has%20supported%20many%20hundreds%20of%20people%20in%20this%20time.%20With%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall%2C%20we%20believe%20we%20can%20deliver%20a%20truly%20exemplary%20project%20embedded%20in%20the%20local%20community%20which%20will%20provide%20a%20route%20for%20many%20more%20people%20out%20of%20homelessness%20for%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20charity's%20chief%20executive%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fai-avatars-will-soon-attend-your-work-meetings-claims-tech-ceo-5085573%5C%22%3E%C2%A0AI%20Avatars%20Will%20Soon%20Attend%20Your%20Work%20Meetings%2C%20Claims%20Tech%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20latest%20announcement%20by%20Prince%20William%20is%20part%20of%20his%20five-year%20campaign%20-%20announced%20in%202023%20-%20to%20end%20homelessness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%2024%20homes%2C%20the%20Duchy%20of%20Cornwall%20also%20confirmed%20its%20future%20housing%20projects%20that%20would%20aim%20to%20increase%20affordable%20housing%20from%2030%25%20to%2040%25%2C%20meaning%20up%20to%20200%20more%20affordable%20homes%20will%20be%20built%20on%20top%20of%20the%20existing%201%2C020%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20It%20also%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20create%20a%20Private%20Rented%20Scheme%20for%20Nansledan%2C%20which%20removes%20barriers%20to%20entry%20for%20those%20on%20lower%20incomes%2C%20provides%20longer-term%20tenancies%20and%20transparent%20rent%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20estate%20committed%20to%20building%20more%20than%20400%20social%20rented%20homes%20and%20a%20further%20475%20affordable%20dwellings%20on%20its%20new%20development