%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20AirSerbia%20Airbus%20A330-200%20aircraft.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20an%20AirSerbia%20Embraer%20E195%20collided%20with%20runway%20lights%20during%20take-off%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20later%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Air%20Serbia%20flight%20knocked%20into%20runway%20lights%20as%20it%20took%20off%20on%20Sunday%2C%20sustaining%20heavy%20damage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20flew%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20before%20finishing%20an%20emergency%20landing%20at%20high%20speed%2C%20flight%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EImages%20on%20social%20media%20of%20the%20damage%20shows%20a%20gashes%20and%20a%20large%20hole%20in%20the%20plane's%20fuselage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20commercial%20jet%20in%20Belgrade%2C%20Serbia%2C%20struck%20a%20set%20of%20runway%20lights%20during%20take-off%20on%20Sunday%2C%20which%20punched%20a%20hole%20into%20its%20fuselage%20that%20forced%20an%20emergency%20landing%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20local%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20Serbia%20flight%20JU324%2C%20operated%20by%20Greek%20carrier%20Marathon%20Airlines%20and%20bound%20for%20D%C3%BCsseldorf%2C%20Germany%2C%20began%20rolling%20for%20take-off%20when%20it%20was%20halfway%20down%20the%20runway%2C%20with%20around%204%2C260%20feet%20of%20space%20to%20accelerate%2C%20per%20Serbian%20aviation%20news%20outlet%20Tango%20Six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20why%20the%20Embraer%20E195LR%20started%20its%20take-off%20with%20a%20shorter%20runway%20distance%2C%20but%20Tango%20Six%20reported%20that%20its%20crew%20told%20flight%20traffic%20control%20they%20were%20confident%20the%20plane%20could%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20Flight%20JU324%20on%20Sunday%20began%20its%20take-off%20roll%20midway%20down%20the%20runway.%20Right%3A%20An%20earlier%20iteration%20of%20the%20same%20flight%20shows%20the%20aircraft%20using%20the%20full%20runway%20length.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d2d11aa610a9069d5a5516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%3A%20Flight%20JU324%20on%20Sunday%20began%20its%20take-off%20roll%20midway%20down%20the%20runway.%20Right%3A%20An%20earlier%20iteration%20of%20the%20same%20flight%20shows%20the%20aircraft%20using%20the%20full%20runway%20length.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%2FFlightRadar24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPlanes%20like%20the%20E195%2C%20which%20generally%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20132%20seats%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aerospace-technology.com%2Fprojects%2Fembraer-e-195-commercial-regional-jet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypically%20need%20around%207%2C000%20feet%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20runway%20to%20take%20off%20comfortably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20E195%20departed%20Belgrade's%20Nikola%20Tesla%20Airport%2C%20the%20bottom%20of%20its%20fuselage%20hit%20a%20set%20of%20runway%20lights%20for%20an%20opposite%20runway%2C%20per%20Tango%20Six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Airbus%20A320-214%20(OO-SNM)%20from%20Brussels%20Airlines%20flying%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20Brussels%20National%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d2d37aa610a9069d5a5527%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223705%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20an%20approach%20lighting%20system%20that%20guides%20aircraft%20for%20the%20runway%2C%3Cp%3EThierry%20Monasse%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20later%20made%20an%20emergency%20landing%20at%20the%20same%20airport%2C%20at%2040%20knots%20faster%20than%20usual%2C%20likely%20because%20its%20flaps%20were%20not%20working%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightradar24.com%2Fdata%2Fflights%2Fju324%23340bbf81%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EData%20from%