overy%20to%20trial%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETailor%20for%20what%20you%20want%3A%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EPick%20your%20battles%20%E2%80%94%20not%20every%20single%20work%20experience%20is%20going%20to%20be%20equal%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%20Because%20he%20was%20applying%20for%20a%20policy%20role%20at%20Google%2C%20he%20says%20he%20should%20have%20emphasized%20his%20policy%20experience%20over%20his%20time%20in%20community%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20all%20negative%2C%20though.%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20appreciate%20about%20this%20resume%20is%20that%20even%20though%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20information%2C%20I%20over%20communicated%20rather%20than%20under-communicated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20worked%20at%20Google's%20policy%20division%20and%20later%20as%20a%20product%20marketing%20manager.%20He%20left%20the%20company%20in%202017%20and%20now%20runs%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40thegooglepmm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness%3C%2Fa%3E%20consulting%20AI%20and%20crypto%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20verified%20Wang's%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-job-resume-regrets-careers-startups-product-marketing-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708311627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce4032a610a9069d59477d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-job-resume-regrets-careers-startups-product-marketing-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Henry%20Wang%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20in%202013%20when%20he%20had%20two%20years%20experience.%20Here's%20how%20he%20did%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A226%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3