2https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faustralian-show-jumper-stood-down-for-competing-in-a-mankini-13074775%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%3A%20More%20Than%20400%20Detained%20at%20Vigils%20for%20Navalny%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12124701%2FEffect-26.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20in%C2%A0Russia%C2%A0have%20detained%20more%20than%20400%20people%20who%20participated%20in%20demonstrations%20held%C2%A0in%20memory%20of%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%C2%A0Alexei%20Navalny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20Navalny%20were%20detained%C2%A0in%2036%20cities%20including%20Moscow%2C%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20and%20Belgorod%20as%20they%20held%20protests%20to%20mark%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20according%20to%20pro-rights%20group%20OVD-Info.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20the%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20allies%2C%20but%20they%20say%20the%20Russian%20government%20is%20refusing%20to%20hand%20over%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBill%20Browder%2C%20the%20American-born%20British%20co-founder%20of%20Hermitage%20Capital%20Management%20and%20an%20adamant%20critic%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20spoke%20to%20DW%20at%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20(MSC)%20about%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrowder%20said%20%E2%80%9CPutin%20killed%20Alexei%20Navalny%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpurpose%20of%20this%20murder%20is%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20anybody%20in%20Russia%20who%E2%80%99s%20even%20thinking%20about%20Vladimir%20Putin%20that%20if%20you%20challenge%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20you%20will%20be%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20targeting%20of%20Navalny%20was%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20going%20to%20suppress%20and%20repress%20the%20Russian%20people%2C%20sadly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Browder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECircumstances%20of%20Navalny%E2%80%99s%20