20saying%20things%20about%20her%20physical%20appearance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20shared%20such%20content%20all%20across%20my%20personal%20social%20media%20page.%20Through%20making%20such%20content%2C%20I%20became%20that%20elder%20sister%20or%20friend%20%5Bto%20my%20followers%5D%20that%20I%20never%20had%20when%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20content%20creator%20to%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98business%20family%E2%80%99%2C%20Diksha%20always%20had%20the%20desire%20to%20start%20one%20herself.%20But%20the%20decision%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202020%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20following%20a%20family%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20was%20experimenting%20with%20fashion%20but%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%20clothes%20%5Bthat%20fit%20my%20size%5D%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20employing%20different%20accessories%20to%20look%20more%20fashionable.%20Even%20while%20travelling%20to%20different%20countries%2C%20particularly%20in%20Asia%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20clothes%20for%20people%20my%20size.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20always%20shop%20for%20jewellery%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20friends%20went%20to%20the%20mall%20and%20shopped%20for%20clothes%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20something%20to%20shop%20for.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20visit%20the%20jewellery%20section%20because%20the%20items%20on%20sale%20there%20did%20not%20come%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20size%20limitations%20you%20see%20in%20apparel%20wear.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20one%20of%20my%20posts%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20people%20writing%20comments%20like%20%E2%80%98Went%20shopping%20for%20clothes%20but%20came%20back%20with%20a%20scrunchie%E2%80%99.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20became%20a%20jewellery%20junkie%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20accessories%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298376%2Fmolbio-diagnostics-truenat-covid-testing-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5BCOVID-19%5D%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20back%20home%20thinking%20about%20what%20to%20do%20next%20with%20my%20life.%20What%20I%20found%20was%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20affordable%20accessories%20segment%20and%20measured%20all%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20associated%20with%20running%20such%20a%20business.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20established%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202020%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20and%20here%20we%20are%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Little%20Extra%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20Little%20Extra%3A%20Diksha%20Singhi%20has%20built%20a%20women-led%20business.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3